Dakota County Office of Geographic Information Systems

Elevation contours exist for Dakota County and are as current as the date of the aerial photography. Two foot contours exist for the urban areas of Dakota County, as well as for Nininger Township, for Lake Byllesby Regional Park and for Miesville Ravine Park Reserve. Ten foot contours exist for the rural areas of Dakota County except for Nininger Township, Lake Byllesby Regional Park and Miesville Ravine Park Reserve.
